pageContext.name: China GES Panel Speaker - CBO Gan Boon San

sections.label: China GES Panel Speaker - CBO Gan Boon San
sections.description:
Boon San, was invited to speak at a panel conference in the Global Educational Summit in China on 26 November 2019. We are proud to have him represented Commontown in an international setting and we aspire to do even more for the edtech industry. 

For more information on the Global Educational Summit 2019, please click here.
